---
import { Github, Linkedin, Mail } from "@lucide/astro";
const { className } = Astro.props;

/*
Efecto de culumna centrada: w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4
md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-4xl lg:px-0
*/
---

<section
  class={`${className} relative w-full h-[100vh]`}
  aria-label="Presentación personal de Enmanuel Bracho"
>
  <!-- Image de fondo -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images4.alphacoders.com/137/thumb-1920-1374662.png')] bg-no-repeat bg-cover"
  >
  </div>

  <!-- Filtro de color -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-base-200/50"></div>

  <div
    class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center mx-auto h-full relative z-5 px-4 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-4xl lg:px-0"
  >
    <header>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-base-content">Enmanuel Bracho</h1>
      <p class="text-3xl text-base-content/60">Frontend Developer</p>
    </header>

    <article aria-label="Descripción personal">
      <p class="text-base-content/60 max-w-lg">
        Actualmente me encuentro estudiando Astro. Soy un desarrollador
        frontend, soy un poco friki, detallista en cuanto al diseño en general
        UX/UI, si me decantará por un paradigma de programación sería sin duda
        el funcional.
      </p>
    </article>

    <footer aria-label="Enlaces personales">
      <nav class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-2" aria-label="Redes sociales">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Enmanuel-VE"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          role="link"
          class="flex flex-row justify-center items-center gap-x-2 bg-base-100/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-black/0 hover:border-primary rounded-full px-4 py-2 cursor-pointer"
          ><Github /><p>GitHub</p></a
        >
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/enmanuel-villanueva-650182353/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          role="link"
          class="flex flex-row justify-center items-center gap-x-2 bg-base-100/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-black/0 hover:border-primary rounded-full px-4 py-2 cursor-pointer"
          ><Linkedin /><p>LinkIn</p></a
        >
        <a
          href="mailto:enmanuel02estudios@gmail.com"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          role="link"
          class="flex flex-row justify-center items-center gap-x-2 bg-base-100/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-black/0 hover:border-primary rounded-full px-4 py-2 cursor-pointer"
          ><Mail /><p>Correo</p></a
        >
      </nav>
    </footer>
  </div>
</section>
